{
  "stem": "3150.3",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The people that I, that I, that we associate, nobody wanted to stay there.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But, you know, they were really pretty well-- Munich was bombed out.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the Germans were really, you know-- you would like to see them struggle, because they really struggled.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I mean, they had no food, and bombed out, and no, and no shelter.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You can see Munich today, but you had to see it in '45 or-- it was like-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] we were just hoping that they, they would never fix it up, but obviously the Marshall Plan did a pretty good job on that one.",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then we, and then we were there-- I was there till '47.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And while we're there, we went to school at a Hebrew school, which I have a picture of it.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And it was normal, very normal life.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You know, you went to school.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "After school, you had facilities, you know, gymnasiums if you wanted to play ball.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We had a soccer team.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It was very, very, very organized.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But we all know it was temporary.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "You know, we got to leave.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, we-- I lived-- my cousin, my cousin was not with us no more.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He, he went to, actually, to a training camp in the area not far away.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He went, he went there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, 16, that's right.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He went there.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He didn't want to-- he did not come there with us.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "My-- the rest of us were together, except, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] except for the, the person that survived with us, which I still can't think of her name right now.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She did not go with us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "She went to a different place, but also to a DP camp.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
